messages.messageBody:
We're going to see Kirby, in Austin! We're leaving in four hours. I
wish I were sleeping, but then again I'm not driving, so I can sleep
tomorrow.

Holly is taking her laptop, but other than putting up pre-prepared
lyrics game entries, I might not be online much or at all.

If you send a post and don't see it, give it many hours or a day. It
might just be waiting for a moderator.

We should be home last Tuesday. If it looks like I'm being accused
of being a slacker or of ignoring people somewhere or other on the
internet, please explain my absence. Someday I will have a laptop,
but today I don't.

http://sandradodd.blogspot.com/2008/04/were-going-to-see-kirby.html
has links to where photos will be in a couple of days.

Sandra
